lead_paragraph: The Chicago Cubs had one of baseball's best lineups during the regular season. Anthony Rizzo and Kris Bryant piled up big numbers, and Ben Zobrist, Dexter Fowler and Addison Russell contributed to a well-rounded attack.

headline.print_headline: Cubs Shut Out Again in World Series, Trail Indians 2-1
